<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="nl">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>PidLane — Jouw auto praat. Wij vertalen.</title>
<meta name="description" content="PidLane leest via OBD2 elke auto uit en vertaalt de data met AI naar een begrijpelijk rapport. Voor consumenten die een auto kopen en voor autobedrijven. Kies je versie.">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
--bg:#0A0E1A;--card:#111827;--card2:#161D2E;--blue:#1A6FFF;--cyan:#00D4FF;
--green:#00FF88;--okgreen:#22C55E;--orange:#FF6B35;--white:#FFFFFF;--mist:#8892A4;--border:#1E2A3E;
--f-display:'Space Grotesk',sans-serif;--f-body:'Inter',sans-serif;--f-mono:'JetBrains Mono',monospace;
}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){html{scroll-behavior:auto}*,*::before,*::after{animation:none!important;transition:none!important}}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--white);font-family:var(--f-body);line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden;min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column}
a:focus-visible,button:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--cyan);outline-offset:3px}
.bg{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse 70% 50% at 50% 30%,rgba(0,255,136,.08) 0%,transparent 65%),radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 50% at 80% 70%,rgba(26,111,255,.10) 0%,transparent 60%),radial-gradient(ellipse 40% 40% at 15% 80%,rgba(0,212,255,.06) 0%,transparent 60%)}
.grid{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:0;background-image:linear-gradient(var(--border) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,var(--border) 1px,transparent 1px);background-size:64px 64px;opacity:.22}
.wrap{position:relative;z-index:1;flex:1;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:64px 24px;max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto;width:100%}
.brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;margin-bottom:30px;animation:rise .6s ease both}
.brand-name{font-family:var(--f-display);font-weight:700;font-size:30px}
.eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;background:rgba(0,255,136,.08);border:1px solid rgba(0,255,136,.25);border-radius:20px;padding:6px 14px;font-size:11px;font-weight:600;color:var(--green);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:22px;animation:rise .6s ease .05s both}
.eyebrow::before{content:'';width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--green);animation:pulse 2s infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}50%{opacity:.4;transform:scale(.7)}}
h1{font-family:var(--f-display);font-size:clamp(34px,5vw,58px);font-weight:700;line-height:1.06;letter-spacing:-.02em;text-align:center;margin-bottom:18px;animation:rise .6s ease .1s both}
h1 span{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--green),var(--cyan));-webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text}
.lead{font-size:17px;color:var(--mist);max-width:620px;text-align:center;line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:14px;animation:rise .6s ease .15s both}
.lead strong{color:var(--white);font-weight:600}
.howline{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:46px;animation:rise .6s ease .2s both}
.chip{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;font-size:12px;color:var(--mist);background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:999px;padding:7px 14px}
.chip b{color:var(--white);font-weight:600}
.choose-label{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--mist);margin-bottom:20px;animation:rise .6s ease .25s both}
.cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:18px;width:100%;animation:rise .6s ease .3s both}
.choice{position:relative;display:flex;flex-direction:column;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:18px;padding:30px;text-decoration:none;color:var(--white);transition:transform .22s ease,border-color .22s ease,box-shadow .22s ease;overflow:hidden}
.choice::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;opacity:0;transition:opacity .22s;pointer-events:none}
.choice:hover{transform:translateY(-4px)}
.choice.consument:hover{border-color:rgba(0,255,136,.45);box-shadow:0 24px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.45)}
.choice.consument::after{background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%,rgba(0,255,136,.10),transparent 70%)}
.choice.zakelijk:hover{border-color:rgba(26,111,255,.5);box-shadow:0 24px 50px rgba(0,0,0,.45)}
.choice.zakelijk::after{background:radial-gradient(ellipse 80% 60% at 50% 0%,rgba(26,111,255,.12),transparent 70%)}
.choice:hover::after{opacity:1}
.ch-ic{width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:24px;margin-bottom:18px}
.consument .ch-ic{background:rgba(0,255,136,.12);border:1px solid rgba(0,255,136,.25)}
.zakelijk .ch-ic{background:rgba(26,111,255,.15);border:1px solid rgba(26,111,255,.3)}
.ch-tag{font-size:10px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:8px}
.consument .ch-tag{color:var(--green)}
.zakelijk .ch-tag{color:#7cacff}
.ch-title{font-family:var(--f-display);font-size:23px;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:8px}
.ch-desc{font-size:14px;color:var(--mist);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:16px}
.ch-li{list-style:none;margin-bottom:22px}
.ch-li li{font-size:12.5px;color:var(--mist);padding:4px 0;display:flex;gap:8px;align-items:flex-start}
.ch-li li::before{content:'\2192';flex-shrink:0}
.consument .ch-li li::before{color:var(--green)}
.zakelijk .ch-li li::before{color:#7cacff}
.ch-go{margin-top:auto;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;font-weight:600;font-size:14px}
.consument .ch-go{color:var(--green)}
.zakelijk .ch-go{color:var(--cyan)}
.more{margin-top:30px;text-align:center;animation:rise .6s ease .38s both}
.more-l{font-size:12px;color:var(--mist);margin-bottom:12px}
.more-tags{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center}
.mt{font-size:12px;color:var(--mist);background:var(--card2);border:1px dashed var(--border);border-radius:999px;padding:7px 14px}
.mt .soon{font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--orange);margin-left:6px}
.more-mail{display:block;margin-top:16px;font-size:13px;color:var(--cyan);text-decoration:none}
.more-mail:hover{text-decoration:underline}
footer{position:relative;z-index:1;padding:20px 24px;border-top:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;font-size:11px;color:var(--mist);text-align:center}
@keyframes rise{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(16px)}to{opacity:1;transform:none}}
@media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.brand,.eyebrow,h1,.lead,.howline,.choose-label,.cards,.more{animation:none}}
@media(max-width:720px){.wrap{padding:48px 18px}.cards{grid-template-columns:1fr}.howline{gap:8px}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="bg"></div><div class="grid"></div>
<main class="wrap">
  <div class="brand">
    <svg width="44" height="34" viewBox="0 0 220 180" aria-hidden="true"><defs><linearGradient id="nlg" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="0"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#00FF88"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#00D4FF"/></linearGradient><linearGradient id="nls" x1="0" y1="0" x2="1" y2="1"><stop offset="0" stop-color="#9D8CFF"/><stop offset="1" stop-color="#00D4FF"/></linearGradient></defs><rect x="12" y="12" width="168" height="118" rx="26" fill="none" stroke="url(#nlg)" stroke-width="13"/><path d="M 36 71 L 66 71 L 80 47 L 100 99 L 116 59 L 126 71 L 158 71" fill="none" stroke="#FFFFFF" stroke-width="11" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/><line x1="96" y1="142" x2="96" y2="158" stroke="#00FF88" stroke-width="10" stroke-linecap="round"/><line x1="96" y1="168" x2="96" y2="178" stroke="#2A3645" stroke-width="9" stroke-linecap="round"/><path d="M 180 -2 C 183 13 188 18 204 22 C 188 26 183 31 180 46 C 177 31 172 26 156 22 C 172 18 177 13 180 -2 Z" fill="url(#nls)"/></svg>
    <span class="brand-name"><span style="color:#fff">Pid</span><span style="color:#00FF88">Lane</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="eyebrow">AI-voertuigdiagnostiek via OBD2</div>
  <h1>Jouw auto praat.<br><span>Wij vertalen.</span></h1>
  <p class="lead">Elke auto van na 2001 heeft een OBD2-poort. PidLane plugt erin, leest de boordcomputer uit en laat <strong>AI de technische data vertalen naar een begrijpelijk rapport</strong> &mdash; met foutcodes in gewone taal, verwachte kosten en een eerlijk advies.</p>
  <div class="howline">
    <span class="chip">&#128268; <b>Inpluggen</b> in OBD2</span>
    <span class="chip">&#128225; <b>Uitlezen</b> live data</span>
    <span class="chip">&#129302; <b>AI-rapport</b> in ~2 min</span>
  </div>
  <div class="choose-label">Voor wie ben je hier?</div>
  <div class="cards">
    <a class="choice consument" href="consument.html">
      <div class="ch-ic">&#128663;</div>
      <div class="ch-tag">Particulier</div>
      <div class="ch-title">PidLane voor consumenten</div>
      <p class="ch-desc">Een auto kopen zonder gokken. Check v&oacute;&oacute;r je betaalt, en houd er daarna een auto-expert in je broekzak op na.</p>
      <ul class="ch-li">
        <li>Aankoop-check: bekende modelproblemen bij die km-stand</li>
        <li>Foutcodes uitlezen in gewone taal</li>
        <li>Klacht uitleggen, oorzaak via meetdata</li>
        <li>Besparingstips op je rijgedrag</li>
      </ul>
      <span class="ch-go">Bekijk de consumentenversie &rarr;</span>
    </a>
    <a class="choice zakelijk" href="zakelijk.html">
      <div class="ch-ic">&#127991;&#65039;</div>
      <div class="ch-tag">Zakelijk &middot; Autobedrijven</div>
      <div class="ch-title">PidLane voor handelaren</div>
      <p class="ch-desc">Verkoop elke occasion met bewijs. Data op de momenten waar het geld zit: inkoop, verkoop en aflevering.</p>
      <ul class="ch-li">
        <li>Inkoopcheck: weet wat je koopt v&oacute;&oacute;r je biedt</li>
        <li>Deelbaar klantrapport (PDF) bij elke auto</li>
        <li>Nulmeting tegen garantiediscussies</li>
        <li>Sterk EV-argument: gemeten accugedrag</li>
      </ul>
      <span class="ch-go">Bekijk de zakelijke versie &rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="more">
    <div class="more-l">Andere afzetmarkten waar PidLane voor in ontwikkeling is:</div>
    <div class="more-tags">
      <span class="mt">Wagenparkbeheer / fleet <span class="soon">binnenkort</span></span>
      <span class="mt">Wegenhulp &amp; autoservice-abonnement <span class="soon">binnenkort</span></span>
      <span class="mt">Lease &amp; taxatie <span class="soon">binnenkort</span></span>
    </div>
    <a class="more-mail" href="mailto:info@pidlane.nl?subject=PidLane%20samenwerking">Interesse in een andere toepassing? info@pidlane.nl</a>
  </div>
</main>
<footer>
  <span>&copy; 2026 PidLane</span>
  <span>&#9889; <em>Your car talks. We translate.</em></span>
  <span>info@pidlane.nl</span>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
